miRNA_targets_hepatocyte

read the hepatocyte RNA-seq data from TableS3 Denzler., et al., 2016

Hepa_expression_data <- read.csv("TableS3_2016_sub.csv",header = TRUE)

count miR-122 target-sites

miR122 = 120000
miR122_6m = 0
miR122_7m = 0
miR122_8m = 0
for (i in 1:9204){
  miR122_6m = miR122_6m+Hepa_expression_data[i,2]*Hepa_expression_data[i,3]
  miR122_7m = miR122_7m+Hepa_expression_data[i,2]*(Hepa_expression_data[i,4]+Hepa_expression_data[i,5])
  miR122_8m = miR122_8m+Hepa_expression_data[i,2]*Hepa_expression_data[i,6]
}
All_FPKM = miR122_6m+miR122_7m+miR122_8m
efficiency = 400000/All_FPKM
miR122_6m = efficiency*miR122_6m
miR122_7m = efficiency*miR122_7m
miR122_8m = efficiency*miR122_8m
Graph<-barplot(c(miR122,miR122_6m,miR122_7m,miR122_8m),names.arg = c("miR122","6mer sites","7mer sites","8mer sites"),main = "miR122 and its target sites per hepatocyte",ylim = c(0,250000))
text(x = Graph, y = c(miR122,miR122_6m,miR122_7m,miR122_8m), label = c(miR122,miR122_6m,miR122_7m,miR122_8m), pos = 3, cex = 0.8, col = "red")
